                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>The <hi rend="smallCaps">JURY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">expressed their admiration of the courageous manner in which Robinson had discharged his duty, and trusted that his conduct would be recognised and rewarded</hi>.</p>
               <p>The <hi rend="smallCaps">COURT</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">concurred in the recommendation of the Jury, and ordered a reward of</hi> 25<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. <hi rend="italic">to be paid to him</hi>.</p>
